summary: Nordic Ruins Camp is just a little player camp I put together real quick
descriptionHtml:
Nordic Ruins Camp is just a little player camp I put together real quick

first uploaded mod, just wanted to share. not much of a describer

-got a tent for your character to sleep in.

-got a smelter, forge, grind stone, work bench, tanning rack, and an alchemy and enchanting table.

-has a light fog around the camp, with some (alot) butterflies fluttering about.

- theres a Sovngarde Watch Statue behind the camp, and when you are close enough to the camp the Sovngarde Chant plays.
author: Arcae
